Document: OpenXRAndroidThreadSettingsExtension
Path: godot/classes/class_openxrandroidthreadsettingsextension.rst
Summary: Wraps the XR_KHR_android_thread_settings extension for Android thread settings in Godot
Inherits: OpenXRExtensionWrapper < Object
Wraps the XR_KHR_android_thread_settings extension. This class provides access to Android-specific thread configuration settings for OpenXR applications, allowing developers to customize thread behavior on Android platforms through the OpenXR API.
